name: Shinzi Katoh 2010 Planner- Cute Hood
description:
This hard to find Shinzi Katoh 2010 Schedule Planner is sold out just about everywhere but here....  at The Paper Bar. This years planner is smaller and more compact than last years model but but it's still loaded with your favorite happy, whimsical, Shinzi Katoh illustrations.

Style: SH4-48 Cute Red Hood

Measures: 15.8 cm x 10.5 cm x 1 cm thick.

Details: Protective vinyl cover, weekly and monthly planning and two color ribbon markers for fast reference.

Note: Whatever is in stock is all that is available for quite awhile. Almost all Shinzi Planners for 2010 are sold out elsewhere.

name: Shinzi Katoh Post Card Gift Set
description:
There's no cuter way to say "hi there!" than with an adorable Shinzi Katoh  illustrated postcard. This wonderful set of 14 postcards comes wrapped in a meter of equally adorable linen sewing tape. Makes a wonderful gift for a friend or... for yourself! Try framing your postcard and hanging it on your wall. Instant art at a low price!

Postcards Designs:  A Cheerful Friend• Fresh Mart• Giggle• Taxi• Rabbit Train• Handstand• Good Luck• Cheri's Many Thanks• For You• Mon Peluche● Forest● Hello!● Happiness● Balloon Rabbit

Dimensions: 4 x 6 inches

Details: Includes 14 Post cards and a meter of 12 mm linen sewing tape that coordinates with bundle. 

NOTE: Post cards are available individually for $2.25/each. Contact me if you are interested in post cards ala' carte!
